<!-- 

background-color : blue

- background-color is property

- : this colon is separator

- blue is value

in styling a color no need to put semi-colon ';' at the end

1. if you add background color at body e.g. <body style = "background-color:blue">

the p style colors will be unable to show

2. some attributes are not working e.g.

<p style = "font-size:40px; color:green font-family = Times New Roman">

-->

